...您的刀，有點太近了......您不會失手吧？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "救、救命啊葦草，我們怎麼辦？！", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......面對這麼多人，很難強行突破。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_singleblunt", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bldwhoosh", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_imp_sword_h", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......啊......棍子被砍斷了？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "葦草", "content": "......他們，很有信心，"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "葦草", "end": "true", "content": "不想暴力抓捕我們，只是想壓制住我們的抵抗。", "joined": "......他們，很有信心，不想暴力抓捕我們，只是想壓制住我們的抵抗。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，這些人的身手也挺不賴的......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我想不明白，能追到這裡，他們是什麼來歷？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——等等，我見過那個人。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在幾天前，我們遇到那一隊“鬼魂士兵”的時候。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼說，你們不是特倫特郡的駐軍，不該越權來逮捕這些流民的。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們這樣不守規矩的話，我們也只好動真格了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“不守規矩”這個詞，對你也一樣適用。既然你的破城矛已經卸掉彈藥，你就應該遠離戰場，士兵。", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，這裡本來就不該是戰場呀？篝火都還沒有熄滅呢......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——小心！", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_atk_knifethrow_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑色的匕首無聲地滑出，尖刃沒有反射出寒光，而是劃出一道煙霧。"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "匕首僅僅威脅性地指向風笛的喉嚨，而握著它的人從始至終，視線都停留在葦草身上。"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草從對方那雙銳利的眼睛裡清晰地讀出，這一切都是衝著自己而來。"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$escape_intro", "key": "$escape_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的長槍上，不該燃燒著火焰嗎？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起徒勞地抵抗，我更希望你能夠明智地選擇放下武器，聽我說明來意。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對塔拉人沒有敵意，更不打算傷害平民以示報復。在保護大眾免於禍端的立場上，我與你們應該是站在一起的。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_scroll", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是政府文件。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，市議會的調查令？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_armour", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前維多利亞士兵放下了手中的武器。"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "依照特倫特郡市議會的決定，我將對一樁縱火案裡被人遺漏的疑點進行調查。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我，沒有別的選擇，對嗎？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_coldforest", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚，嗚嗚......", "name": "年幼的塔拉流民"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——幹什麼？安靜點。", "name": "看守士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_catsmell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......（抽泣）", "name": "年幼的塔拉流民"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（唉，真難受。）", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#2$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我過去一直想，要死的話，至少該先寫好遺書......）", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（要我說，你早該寫了。）", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（剛逃出來的時候是寫了一封，這兩天高興過頭了，撕掉了。我真後悔。）", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（閉嘴，維恩。我們還沒完蛋呢。）", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（人都被綁起來了，能拿來打架的東西也被收走了，我們除了等死還能做什麼？）", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（唉......審訊，審訊這個詞多嚇人啊。被審訊的塔拉人，我們聽說過的，有幾個活著回來過？）", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（葦草那麼心善的人，也不知道他們要從她那裡問出什麼。）", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我們這些人，互相都是知根知底的，可是葦草她從哪裡來，以前幹了什麼事，我們沒人知道。）", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（怎麼，你敢懷疑她？）", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不不不，我哪有這個意思呀......我只是......）", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（唉，塞爾蒙，你總不能不許人怕死吧。）", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（從這裡還能看到篝火的光呢，我們有多少天沒見過夜裡的火光了？）", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我真的以為自己逃出來了。）", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（你還找我商量，借點什麼東西做本錢。我是不是答應做一批燻羽獸肉給你拿去賣？）", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（別說了。我們要想辦法去看看情況。）", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（啊，怎麼看？再說，看了又有什麼用？）", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......我就是不甘心。）", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我就是不喜歡聽你只能一個勁地歎氣。我蹲在塔拉人街區的路口，或者穿過村子的打穀場的時候......到處都是歎氣聲。我聽膩了。）", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（行了，別廢話，別問我怎麼辦，你明明每次都能自己想出辦法。）", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我去吸引那幾個看守的注意力，你該做什麼，自己想去。）", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g10_tent_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodcracle", "volume": 0.1}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以放鬆一點，“葦草”，我們只是普通地聊聊天。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一堆溫暖的篝火，還能聽到夜間羽獸的鳴叫，我想這樣的環境比真正的審訊室要愜意許多。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉默？你也可以選擇沉默，我不會為難你。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許之前鄰近地區駐軍有失尊重的行事方式讓你產生了戒心，我替他們向你道歉。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你是想調查深池的事情嗎？這裡所有人都與深池無關......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用解釋，這些情況我當然已經掌握。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個小地方的駐軍確實會因為一場襲擊而對十幾個塔拉人過分計較，隨意加以“深池反叛軍”的罪名。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這厚厚的卷宗裡，他們犯的錯誤不值一提。當然，你與其他人的情況稍有不同......", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......但我也能想辦法幫助你擺脫這些麻煩。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，這一路逃亡，應該很不容易。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......如果沒有那些嚴苛的律令，他們從一開始，就不需要逃跑。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，既然是我們二人之間的閒聊，我希望你說說你自己的事。說說你從更早以前就開始的逃亡。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不明白你在說什麼。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "菲舍爾", "content": "我在問你，"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "菲舍爾", "delay": 0.07, "content": "曾經的身份。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個普通人，沒有任何檔案記錄，醫療體檢、進出移動城市、繳納稅金，什麼都沒有。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......塔拉人常常被驅趕，維多利亞的記錄裡看不到我們，不奇怪。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，去年秋天小丘郡動亂的時候，你在那裡嗎？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去年五月半島郡遭受襲擊的時候，你在那裡嗎？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我問的只是你。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，如果一個人自己都說不出自己本來的名字，說不出自己從哪裡來，是什麼人的話......", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不是，就像“影子”一樣？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g9_tent", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳陳，你是不是大概猜到這些人的身份了？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。方才與我們交手的並非普通士兵，就地審訊也是很特殊的做法。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再加上，那個帶頭的人知道很多，才會對我們......對我如此客氣。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對欸。我剛剛還在想，他們可以讓我們站在這裡等著，只是讓人看守，但那些塔拉人就要把雙手綁起來，好不公平......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可他是怎麼認出來你的呀？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我沒想到情報部門的人會出動。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情報部門？情報部門為什麼會找上葦草？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她應該身份特殊。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以她之前執意獨自行動，不想牽連誰。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，我有種不好的感覺......他們真的會好好跟一個塔拉人溝通嗎？他們會不會打她，或者威脅她說違心的話？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "輕聲些。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯，我還記得你那份關於小丘郡的報告書是怎麼寫的。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是呀，雖然那個人有市議會的調查令，也說了會和平溝通，對塔拉人沒有敵意什麼的，但......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不對，我還是應該相信，他是議會決定的執行者，不會亂來。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但審訊的壓力，一般人扛不過去。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#3$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你記不記得上學的時候，我們兩人搭檔，是怎麼行動的？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，你這個手勢......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得。那次搶奪高危源石製品的時候，我們用過這套手勢交流。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記得就好。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草她無論是什麼特殊身份，只要落在他人手裡作為棋子，恐怕都會給現下的局勢帶來不小的風波。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，她自己也一定會很難過......畢竟她看起來，好像一直想要甩掉自己身上的什麼東西。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白你的意思了，陳陳。我們幫她回羅德島。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g4_swamp_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowswalk", "volume": 0.7, "loop": "true", "channel": "walksp"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#7$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "walksp", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀......真是清晰的車轍。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你的對手又在邀請你。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#7$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這麼揶揄我。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜，這一次，我恐怕還擔不起“邀請”這個詞，他甚至不會在乎他的客人要跳一支怎樣的舞。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們露面這件事，本身就足以說明我們的立場了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深池去救可憐的拉芙希妮，會暴露她的身份......也會最終證明我站在哪一邊。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而他也知道，為了不讓另一條塔拉的德拉克落入他背後那位公爵手中，降低領袖她德拉克這一身份的影響力......我不得不去。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無妨，我會把他的野心清掃乾淨。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g10_tent_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......羽獸的叫聲停止了。你知道這意味著什麼嗎？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......（搖頭）", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，先來說說你近期留下的案件記錄吧。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒有對他人造成過嚴重傷害。就連那起發生在駐軍處的火災，也只有一些儲備物資被燒毀，沒有任何人員傷亡。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一般塔拉人對維多利亞駐軍的仇恨犯罪不會如此。相比之下，你的做法很溫和。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至有目擊者指出你嘗試擊退深池士兵。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些，你承認嗎？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只承認，我的確不想傷害他人。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我可以相信，你是有相當良知的人。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，關於那些變得安靜的羽獸......", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是你深池的朋友們來救你了。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......不。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能回去......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回去？哦，你是說，回到作為影子的生活？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回到那種被燃燒的屍體包圍、將死者的灰燼灑滿城市街道的生活？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於一個有良知的人而言，那樣的生活想必十分痛苦。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在你恰好有機會，可以做出屬於你自己的選擇。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接受我們的庇護，你過去犯下的罪行不會被追究。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "葦草", "content": "我......"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "ra